<plot>This stylized sci-fi short thriller tells the story of Bat, a blind film projectionist, whose quest for sight comes at a high price. Bat lives in the world of his own imagination, dreaming of seeing the movies he projects. When a dubious opportunity to regain his sight arrives, Bat finds it too tempting to miss. A submission that could prove fatal.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?414906</url></doc>
